name: UNRAVELED
description:
(5/5) Social Norms and Misjudgments

Collect all 5 pieces to be airdropped the 6th and final mint of this collection! 

She shed her fears and crawled out from the hole that was made for her. She understood that life is unfair and nothing is given, so she escaped the path that was laid upon. 

Model: Luisa I. Short  

This mint is created to help spread awareness and make meaningful impacts on those who need it within the community. This is a conceptual series related to the stereotypes and social norms we see in our daily lives.
